{
  "font_size": 0.4,
  "font_color": "#FFFFFF",
  "background_alpha": 0.5,
  "background_color": "#9C27B0",
  "Stroke": "none",
  "type": "AIsubtitle",
  "lang": "zh",
  "version": "eng-1.2.0-Index-johns-pen-lite",
  "body": [
    {
      "content": "人们和企业做了很多事情",
      "from": 0.04,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 1,
      "to": 4.21
    },
    {
      "content": "如何将我们所做的这些有用的事情",
      "from": 4.21,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 2,
      "to": 6.87
    },
    {
      "content": "分解成离散步骤供enworkflow执行",
      "from": 6.87,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 3,
      "to": 11.82
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们看看",
      "from": 11.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 4,
      "to": 12.76
    },
    {
      "content": "以构建研究代理为例",
      "from": 12.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 5,
      "to": 15.72
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你想让AI系统撰写某个主题的论文",
      "from": 15.72,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 6,
      "to": 19.56
    },
    {
      "content": "你可以直接提示它生成输出结果",
      "from": 19.56,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 7,
      "to": 24.09
    },
    {
      "content": "但若处理需要深度研究的主题时",
      "from": 24.09,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 8,
      "to": 28.55
    },
    {
      "content": "可能会发现输出仅涵盖表面内容",
      "from": 28.55,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 9,
      "to": 32.29
    },
    {
      "content": "或者只包含显而易见的事实",
      "from": 32.29,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 10,
      "to": 34.56
    },
    {
      "content": "但未能深入探讨你希望的层面",
      "from": 34.56,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 11,
      "to": 38.64
    },
    {
      "content": "在这种情况下",
      "from": 38.64,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 12,
      "to": 39.4
    },
    {
      "content": "你可能会反思作为人类",
      "from": 39.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 13,
      "to": 42.76
    },
    {
      "content": "我们如何撰写特定主题的论文",
      "from": 42.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 14,
      "to": 45.0
    },
    {
      "content": "我们只需坐下开始写作",
      "from": 45.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 15,
      "to": 46.84
    },
    {
      "content": "还是需要分步骤进行",
      "from": 46.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 16,
      "to": 48.54
    },
    {
      "content": "例如先撰写论文大纲",
      "from": 48.54,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 17,
      "to": 50.7
    },
    {
      "content": "然后进行网络搜索",
      "from": 50.7,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 18,
      "to": 51.9
    },
    {
      "content": "然后根据网络搜索结果",
      "from": 51.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 19,
      "to": 54.14
    },
    {
      "content": "撰写论文",
      "from": 54.14,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 20,
      "to": 55.18
    },
    {
      "content": "当我拆解任务为步骤时",
      "from": 55.18,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 21,
      "to": 58.8
    },
    {
      "content": "我始终在问自己",
      "from": 58.8,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 22,
      "to": 60.96
    },
    {
      "content": "如果观察这些步骤",
      "from": 60.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 23,
      "to": 62.0
    },
    {
      "content": "每个步骤（一、二、三）是否",
      "from": 62.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 24,
      "to": 66.57
    },
    {
      "content": "可以由语言模型处理",
      "from": 66.57,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 25,
      "to": 69.05
    },
    {
      "content": "或由简短代码完成",
      "from": 69.05,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 26,
      "to": 71.259
    },
    {
      "content": "或通过工具调用函数",
      "from": 71.259,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 27,
      "to": 75.33
    },
    {
      "content": "在这种情况下，我认为语言模型可能能生成不错的提纲",
      "from": 75.33,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 28,
      "to": 79.59
    },
    {
      "content": "对于我需要它协助分析的许多主题",
      "from": 79.59,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 29,
      "to": 81.48
    },
    {
      "content": "在第一步",
      "from": 81.48,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 30,
      "to": 82.12
    },
    {
      "content": "我知道如何用语言模型生成搜索关键词",
      "from": 82.12,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 31,
      "to": 87.3
    },
    {
      "content": "因此第二步也是可行的",
      "from": 87.3,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 32,
      "to": 89.48
    },
    {
      "content": "然后基于网络搜索结果",
      "from": 89.48,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 33,
      "to": 91.18
    },
    {
      "content": "我认为大语言模型可以输入搜索结果并撰写论文",
      "from": 91.18,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 34,
      "to": 94.52
    },
    {
      "content": "这将是撰写论文的合理初步工作流",
      "from": 94.52,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 35,
      "to": 99.49
    },
    {
      "content": "比直接生成更深入",
      "from": 99.49,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 36,
      "to": 102.789
    },
    {
      "content": "但当我实施此工作流并查看结果时",
      "from": 102.789,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 37,
      "to": 107.04
    },
    {
      "content": "可能会发现结果仍不够理想",
      "from": 107.04,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 38,
      "to": 109.68
    },
    {
      "content": "思考深度仍不足",
      "from": 109.68,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 39,
      "to": 111.94
    },
    {
      "content": "论文可能显得有些零散",
      "from": 111.94,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 40,
      "to": 114.52
    },
    {
      "content": "实际上，当我曾构建过使用此工作流的研究代理时",
      "from": 114.52,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 41,
      "to": 118.28
    },
    {
      "content": "但当我阅读输出结果",
      "from": 118.28,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 42,
      "to": 119.42
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉有些零散",
      "from": 119.42,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 43,
      "to": 120.72
    },
    {
      "content": "文章开头与中间部分不完全连贯",
      "from": 120.72,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 44,
      "to": 124.38
    },
    {
      "content": "与整体内容不完全一致",
      "from": 124.38,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 45,
      "to": 126.87
    },
    {
      "content": "此时你可能需要反思如何调整工作流",
      "from": 126.87,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 46,
      "to": 131.35
    },
    {
      "content": "作为人类发现论文略显零散时",
      "from": 131.35,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 47,
      "to": 134.78
    },
    {
      "content": "可以将第三步进一步拆解",
      "from": 134.78,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 48,
      "to": 139.8
    },
    {
      "content": "将论文撰写分解为更多步骤",
      "from": 139.8,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 49,
      "to": 142.709
    },
    {
      "content": "因此不再一次性完成整篇论文撰写",
      "from": 142.709,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 50,
      "to": 145.889
    },
    {
      "content": "你可能拥有另一种方式",
      "from": 145.889,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 51,
      "to": 147.169
    },
    {
      "content": "先写出初稿",
      "from": 147.169,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 52,
      "to": 148.37
    },
    {
      "content": "然后考虑哪些部分需要修改",
      "from": 148.37,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 53,
      "to": 150.75
    },
    {
      "content": "接着修订以推进",
      "from": 150.75,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 54,
      "to": 152.19
    },
    {
      "content": "这就是我作为人类可能处理的方式",
      "from": 152.19,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 55,
      "to": 155.63
    },
    {
      "content": "不仅仅在第一次尝试就写出最终论文",
      "from": 155.63,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 56,
      "to": 159.45
    },
    {
      "content": "而是先写初稿然后通读",
      "from": 159.45,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 57,
      "to": 161.8
    },
    {
      "content": "这也是相当有效的一个步骤",
      "from": 161.8,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 58,
      "to": 165.6
    },
    {
      "content": "然后基于我对自己的论文的批判",
      "from": 165.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 59,
      "to": 168.02
    },
    {
      "content": "我会修订草稿",
      "from": 168.02,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 60,
      "to": 169.5
    },
    {
      "content": "所以回顾开始时我直接生成",
      "from": 169.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 61,
      "to": 172.98
    },
    {
      "content": "仅一步完成",
      "from": 172.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 62,
      "to": 174.38
    },
    {
      "content": "但觉得还不够好",
      "from": 174.38,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 63,
      "to": 175.92
    },
    {
      "content": "于是分解为三个步骤",
      "from": 175.92,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 64,
      "to": 178.1
    },
    {
      "content": "可能仍觉得不够完善",
      "from": 178.1,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 65,
      "to": 180.1
    },
    {
      "content": "将其中一个步骤进一步拆分",
      "from": 180.1,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 66,
      "to": 183.05
    },
    {
      "content": "或分解为三个更细的步骤",
      "from": 183.05,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 67,
      "to": 185.73
    },
    {
      "content": "形成更复杂的",
      "from": 185.73,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 68,
      "to": 187.88
    },
    {
      "content": "更丰富的论文生成流程",
      "from": 187.88,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 69,
      "to": 191.22
    },
    {
      "content": "根据对这一流程结果的满意度",
      "from": 191.22,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 70,
      "to": 195.29
    },
    {
      "content": "甚至可能进一步调整生成流程",
      "from": 195.29,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 71,
      "to": 199.75
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们看第二个分解复杂任务的例子",
      "from": 199.75,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 72,
      "to": 205.829
    },
    {
      "content": "以处理基本客户订单咨询为例",
      "from": 205.829,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 73,
      "to": 210.149
    },
    {
      "content": "人类客服机构可能执行的第一步",
      "from": 210.149,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 74,
      "to": 213.249
    },
    {
      "content": "可能是提取关键信息",
      "from": 213.249,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 75,
      "to": 216.06
    },
    {
      "content": "例如发件人是谁",
      "from": 216.06,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 76,
      "to": 218.0
    },
    {
      "content": "他们订购了什么",
      "from": 218.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 77,
      "to": 219.02
    },
    {
      "content": "以及订单号是什么",
      "from": 219.02,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 78,
      "to": 220.68
    },
    {
      "content": "这些都可以处理",
      "from": 220.68,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 79,
      "to": 223.49
    },
    {
      "content": "我可以直接这样做",
      "from": 223.49,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 80,
      "to": 225.43
    },
    {
      "content": "第二步是查找相关客户记录",
      "from": 225.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 81,
      "to": 229.01
    },
    {
      "content": "编写并生成相关数据库查询",
      "from": 229.01,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 82,
      "to": 232.72
    },
    {
      "content": "调取客户的订单信息",
      "from": 232.72,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 83,
      "to": 235.16
    },
    {
      "content": "以及发货时间等",
      "from": 235.16,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 84,
      "to": 236.5
    },
    {
      "content": "我认为在具备函数调用能力的LM中",
      "from": 236.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 85,
      "to": 239.98
    },
    {
      "content": "执行查询",
      "from": 239.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 86,
      "to": 241.329
    },
    {
      "content": "应能直接调用订单数据库",
      "from": 241.329,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 87,
      "to": 244.409
    },
    {
      "content": "最后在获取客户记录或订单记录后",
      "from": 244.409,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 88,
      "to": 248.109
    },
    {
      "content": "我可能撰写并回复客户",
      "from": 248.109,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 89,
      "to": 251.37
    },
    {
      "content": "结合我们获取的信息",
      "from": 251.37,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 90,
      "to": 253.31
    },
    {
      "content": "第三步也能用LM完成",
      "from": 253.31,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 91,
      "to": 256.0
    },
    {
      "content": "如果提供调用API发送邮件的选项",
      "from": 256.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 92,
      "to": 259.5
    },
    {
      "content": "这就是分解客户邮件回复任务的例子",
      "from": 259.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 93,
      "to": 264.65
    },
    {
      "content": "拆分为三个独立步骤",
      "from": 264.65,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 94,
      "to": 267.39
    },
    {
      "content": "我可以逐一检查这些步骤",
      "from": 267.39,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 95,
      "to": 269.49
    },
    {
      "content": "我认为具备函数调用能力的LM",
      "from": 269.49,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 96,
      "to": 273.26
    },
    {
      "content": "能查询数据库或发送邮件",
      "from": 273.26,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 97,
      "to": 275.26
    },
    {
      "content": "应能完成这些操作",
      "from": 275.26,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 98,
      "to": 276.5
    },
    {
      "content": "最后一个发票处理示例",
      "from": 276.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 99,
      "to": 279.72
    },
    {
      "content": "PDF发票转换为文本后",
      "from": 279.72,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 100,
      "to": 282.74
    },
    {
      "content": "第一步是提取所需信息",
      "from": 282.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 101,
      "to": 285.86
    },
    {
      "content": "账单名称",
      "from": 285.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 102,
      "to": 286.92
    },
    {
      "content": "地址",
      "from": 286.92,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 103,
      "to": 287.7
    },
    {
      "content": "到期日期",
      "from": 287.7,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 104,
      "to": 288.48
    },
    {
      "content": "应付金额等等",
      "from": 288.48,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 105,
      "to": 289.8
    },
    {
      "content": "现在我应该能够完成这个操作",
      "from": 289.8,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 106,
      "to": 291.44
    },
    {
      "content": "然后如果我想检查信息是否已提取",
      "from": 291.44,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 107,
      "to": 295.54
    },
    {
      "content": "并保存到新数据库条目中",
      "from": 295.54,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 108,
      "to": 297.7
